173
00:07:36,930 --> 00:07:38,632
TCHAU, SR. KERWIN...

174
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,867
TCHAU, SR. KERWIN.

175
00:07:46,807 --> 00:07:48,108
TOBY?

176
00:07:49,810 --> 00:07:51,711
TOBY! AQUI!

177
00:07:51,745 --> 00:07:52,746
TOBES.

178
00:08:00,821 --> 00:08:02,622
O QUE VOCÊ ESTÁ FAZENDO?

179
00:08:02,956 --> 00:08:05,559
EVITANDO A LIBERTY.

180
00:08:05,592 --> 00:08:07,761
E A SUA ENTREVISTA?

181
00:08:07,794 --> 00:08:09,596
